reviews.review_text: Great Show Outstanding recording of a superior show. Entire second set, especially post He's Gone, is amazing featuring stellar Garcia and Hornsby interplay.

Happy to have it But the recording is just ok and their performance is pretty poor (sorry y'all, just calling them as i see them).
I was at the show and it felt much better than it sounds listening. Lots of bummer notes and such.
